# Tok Overview

Tok is a macOS app that allows you to transcribe your voice into text with a global hotkey. 
Tok will paste the transcription into your current app.


- Swift Composable Architecture
- Swift 6
- Swift Async/Await


The name of the build schema is `Tok`

`xcodebuild -project Hex.xcodeproj -scheme Tok -configuration Debug build`